  <p><strong>Quick Answer:</strong> Rosé wine works exceptionally well with Mediterranean cuisine, grilled vegetables, seafood, and light summer dishes. The wine's crisp acidity and subtle fruit flavors complement fresh ingredients without overwhelming delicate flavors, making it ideal for outdoor dining and warm-weather meals.</p>
